gw.plugin.billing

Interface BillingInvoiceInfo


  • public interface BillingInvoiceInfo
    The BillingInvoiceInfo class provides:
    • The InvoiceDate as a Date
    • The InvoiceDueDate as a Date
    • The Amount as a MonetaryAmount
    • The Paid as a MonetaryAmount
    • The Billed as a MonetaryAmount
    • The PastDue as a MonetaryAmount
    • The Unpaid as a MonetaryAmount
    • The InvoiceNumber as a String
    • The PaidStatus as a String
    • The Status as a String
    • The InvoiceStream as a String
